continues to arrive from Armenia.''
   He said he shared in the grief of the suffering and prayed for
the Armenian people ``in this painful moment of their history.''
   Italian President Francesco Cossiga sent a message expressing his
sorrow to Soviet leader Mikhail S. Gorbachev.
